                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-166" type="given" value="WILLIAM EDWARD"></interp>WILLIAM EDWARD ARCHBUTT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, at Bridge-road, Lambeth. This chain was pledged by the prisoner.</p>
